<p>I have had this small list of universes in which the Foundation could be considered involved or in-universe, besides post-apocalyptic media (_K-Class Scenarios). I've been wanting to share it for some time, and this is the perfect forum to do so on. I won't go into too much detail, just a quick explanation of why they may be related.</p>
<p><strong>Shrek:</strong> Lord Farquaad (The Foundation) is attempting to relocate and/or minimize the presence of &quot;fairy tale creatures&quot; (SCP's) in the normal world.</p>
<p><strong>The X-Files:</strong> UIU? Some other GOI that investigates anomalies?</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
